divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: Oh my fucking god I just saw a fucking UFO outside. I was giving my dog her food and I hear this sound. It wasn t a loud sound more like a soft sound, it sounded like "loooooo". I look up and there s these lights I can see through the clouds. It s cloudy right now I could only see the lights, 2 lights were white facing opposite to eachother, other 2 lights were going in a circle around themselves and were red and greeen, there were another 2 lighs that were also swirling around themselves and were facing opposite to the other 2, and they were also red and green. IT was like a square made of lights but you could only see the corners. I was so shocked when I saw it I just started up and didn t move until it wasn t visible anymore. It just disappeared into the clouds, it s very cloudy right now which is rare here in Phoenix Arizona. I came to my senses when my dog jumped on me and then I came inside to report this.
Summary: Square made of 6 lights in the sky
